trans-unit.source: Represents a configuration element that specifies a certificate used by a client.
trans-unit.target: 表示組態項目，指定用戶端的憑證。

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: 這個類別無法被繼承。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Configuration.X509ClientCertificateCredentialsElement"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化的新執行個體<xref href="System.ServiceModel.Configuration.X509ClientCertificateCredentialsElement"></xref>類別。

trans-unit.source: Copies the content of the specified configuration element to this configuration element.
trans-unit.target: 將指定的組態項目的內容複製到這個組態項目。

trans-unit.source: The configuration element to be copied.
trans-unit.target: 要複製的組態元素。

trans-unit.source: from is .
trans-unit.target: fromis .

trans-unit.source: The configuration file is read-only.
trans-unit.target: 組態檔為唯讀。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a string that specifies the value to search for in the X.509 certificate store.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定字串，指定要在 X.509 憑證存放區中搜尋的值。

trans-unit.source: The type contained in this property must satisfy the requirements of the specified <xref:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.X509ClientCertificateCredentialsElement.X509FindType%2A> value.
trans-unit.target: 這個屬性所包含型別必須滿足指定之需求<xref:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.X509ClientCertificateCredentialsElement.X509FindType%2A>值。</xref:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.X509ClientCertificateCredentialsElement.X509FindType%2A>

trans-unit.source: The default is an empty string.
trans-unit.target: 預設為空字串。

trans-unit.source: The value to search for in the X.509 certificate store.
trans-unit.target: 要在 X.509 憑證存放區中搜尋的值。

trans-unit.source: To be added.
trans-unit.target: 即將加入。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that specifies the location of the certificate store that the service can use to validate the client's certificate.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定值，這個值會指定服務可用來驗證用戶端憑證的憑證存放區位置。

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.StoreLocation"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.StoreLocation"></xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default value is <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.StoreLocation"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 預設值是<xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.StoreLocation"> </xref>。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the name of the X.509 certificate store to open.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定要開啟的 X.509 憑證存放區的名稱。

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.StoreName"></xref> that contains the name of the X.509 certificate store to open.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.StoreName"> </xref> ，其中包含要開啟的 X.509 憑證存放區的名稱。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the type of X.509 search to be executed.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定要執行 X.509 搜尋的型別。

trans-unit.source: The type contained in <xref:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.X509ClientCertificateCredentialsElement.FindValue%2A> must satisfy the requirements of this property.
trans-unit.target: 中包含的型別<xref:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.X509ClientCertificateCredentialsElement.FindValue%2A>必須滿足這個屬性的需求。</xref:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.X509ClientCertificateCredentialsElement.FindValue%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509FindType"></xref> that specifies the type of X.509 search to be executed.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509FindType"> </xref> ，指定要執行 X.509 搜尋類型。
